>\n(不過客運好似都係好遠)"},{"pid":"1fcd84d5145b0428f7c5832cbb6242b622afe7e3","tid":385192,"uid":38648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"搭台鐵三個鐘上到台北 好似一百蚊港紙到"},{"pid":"962c23932cc28d11847ba7572c4d28480542687a","tid":385192,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你去幾多日 短就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa102b60a9abdbf344c90e9ba8dd54d22cd15226","tid":385192,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去幾多日 短就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台中啦就咁"},{"pid":"d9382e358a5685204c2ecd241988685624880797","tid":385192,"uid":74985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去幾多日 短就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩下台中<br />\n去下清境阿里山都夠你玩"},{"pid":"262f84cf8ba9d8503dd9564e3368340d256f0030","tid":385192,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去幾多日 短就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得三日，留台中算啦<br />\n如果你都係想上台北，最平係客運，大約三個鐘車程，同埋班次都幾密，我覺得好過搭火車"},{"pid":"7fe5a00a3d0945dc5a216493bdcf58cc2144c7e8","tid":385192,"uid":31031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去幾多日 短就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad